<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 08 at 9:22AM CST  by NWS Brownsville</headline>
<description>...DENSE FOG LINGERS NEAR THE COAST...
Surface observations and webcams indicate that pockets of dense
fog reducing visibility to a quarter mile or less remain in place
in some Cameron County and coastal locations this morning. South
Padre Island, Bayview, and Harlingen indicated dense fog. The fog
will burn off later today, but will persist through late this
morning at some spots.
Motorists are urged to reduce speed, use low beam headlights, and
avoid following other cars too closely in the fog.</description>
